Just cram it, would you!

36
00:02:52,545 --> 00:02:53,780
Whether it works against me or not,

37
00:02:53,780 --> 00:02:55,382
as long as I beat him,
nothing else matters!

38
00:02:55,382 --> 00:02:57,183
Stay out of the way!
Who the hell are you!?

39
